lled vinegar, molasses, corn syrup, salt, caramel color, garlic powder, sugar, spices(celery seed), tamarind, natural flavor, sulphite), silicon dioxide), canola oil, citric acid, herbs, sodium diacetate, silicon dioxide (anti-caking agent), natural flavor) (sulphites) • White wine vinegar (wine vinegar, potassium metabisulfite) (sulphites) • Dill-garlic spice blend (dehydrated onion, dehydrated garlic, salt, dill weed, canola oil, silicon dioxide) (sulphites).
